title: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
description: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown. Steps to reproduce: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Attempt to export data in the table inside a grid cell.
OB: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The expected result is that the data in the table is exported successfully.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Attempt to export data in the table inside a grid cell.
